00:00:03,837 --> 00:00:06,715
Welcome to the Principles of
Lift Truck Safety.

2
00:00:06,715 --> 00:00:10,010
In this class, We'll be
covering the basics of
safely operating a lift truck.

3
00:00:10,010 --> 00:00:12,220
This includes all
safety-related information,

4
00:00:12,220 --> 00:00:14,431
as well as the operational
essentials you need to know.

5
00:00:14,431 --> 00:00:18,143
The purpose of this class is
to teach you the safety rules,
concepts, and guidelines

6
00:00:18,184 --> 00:00:21,229
required for operating a lift
truck at The Home Depot.


7
00:00:21,229 --> 00:00:25,066
Once you complete this class,
you'll move on to the web based
training specific to the equipment

8
00:00:25,108 --> 00:00:28,737
you'll be licensed to operate.
Then, you'll go through the
hands-on portion of this


9
00:00:28,778 --> 00:00:30,822
curriculum, which leads
to licensing.

10
00:00:30,822 --> 00:00:32,699
So, if you're ready,
let's get started.
